snippet.title: Waddle Knight Trailer
snippet.description:
The trailer for the Kirby fangame, Waddle Knight, a boss-focused platformer with gameplay inspired by Hollow Knight and Cuphead!

Check out the first Waddle Knight, it's fully completed!
https://waddledev.itch.io/waddle-knight
https://gamejolt.com/games/waddleknight/837356

Waddle Knight 2: Pantheon Demo, the 30 boss demo, is out now!
https://waddledev.itch.io/waddle-knight-2-pantheon-demo
https://gamejolt.com/games/waddleknight2demo/942404

Check out Strimp's Kitchen Discord!
https://discord.gg/RUNXx8QC
